To scale the NGINX cluster, just perform a normal upgrade setting the *replicaCount* value to the desired number of nodes. For example, use the command below to scale the cluster up to three replicas:

~~~
$ helm upgrade bitnami/nginx \
  --set replicaCount=3
~~~
